flip7-blueshadow-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/012-combo-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-Zflip7-blueshadow-550x366.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/012-combo-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-Zflip7-blueshadow-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/012-combo-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-Zflip7-blueshadow-1160x773.jpg 1160w\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Samsung\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you choose to buy Samsung\u0026#39;s new foldables straight from Amazon, maybe because it is more convenient, you won\u0026#39;t get such a wealth of savings options, but there\u0026#39;ll be a gift card included with each new model, and that might be enough. The double storage promotion applies with Amazon too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ctable\u003e\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhone\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAmazon Gift Card Value\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSamsung Galaxy Z Fold 7\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e$300\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSamsung Galaxy Z Flip 7\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e$200\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSamsung Galaxy Z Flip 7 FE\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e$100\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"t-mobile\"\u003eT-Mobile\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy Z Fold/Flip 7 Pre-Order Deals From Samsung, Carriers, More 7\" srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack.jpg 1620w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-1300x867.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-550x367.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-1160x773.jpg 1160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1620px) 100vw, 1620px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;1620\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1080\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201620%201080\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack.jpg 1620w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-1300x867.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-550x367.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/010-family-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-silvershadow-jetblack-1160x773.jpg 1160w\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Samsung\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you prefer to buy your devices with a carrier, as opposed to unlocked, then T-Mobile has something for you. \u003ca href=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/511085-tmobile-dashpass-free/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/511085-tmobile-dashpass-free/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eT-Mobile\u003c/a\u003e is the only carrier that will give you double the storage for free, but with some additional perks on top of that.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e$1,100 off the Z Fold 7 or the Z Flip 7 for free, if you add a line or trade in an eligible device in any condition. However, this applies only to the Experience More, Experience Beyond plans, and their business equivalents.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e$1,000 off the Z Fold 7 or Z Flip 7 when trading in a device AND adding a line on Business Unlimited Ultimate.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e$600 off the Z Fold 7 or Z Flip 7 when adding a line on most plans.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e$500 off when trading in a device on most plans.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"att\"\u003eAT\u0026amp;T\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy Z Fold/Flip 7 Pre-Order Deals From Samsung, Carriers, More 8\" srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow.jpg 1620w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-1300x867.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-550x367.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-1160x773.jpg 1160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1620px) 100vw, 1620px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;1620\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1080\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201620%201080\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow.jpg 1620w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-1300x867.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-550x367.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/019-handson-galaxy-zflip7-blueshadow-1160x773.jpg 1160w\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Samsung\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/505466-us-carriers-tariff-costs/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/505466-us-carriers-tariff-costs/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eAT\u0026amp;T\u003c/a\u003e won\u0026#39;t sit around and let T-Mobile get all the spotlight for its deals on the new Samsung foldables. This carrier has some sweet offers too, though it drops some, like the double storage promo.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt will give you $1,100 off the Z Fold 7 or the Z Flip 7 for free, as long as you trade in an eligible phone, regardless of the year or condition of the device.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt will also give you a special triple bundle offer. When you buy the Z Fold or Flip 7, you will be able to add a Galaxy Watch 8 and a Tab A9+ 5G for only $0.99 each.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"verizon\"\u003eVerizon\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy Z Fold/Flip 7 Pre-Order Deals From Samsung, Carriers, More 9\" srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow.jpg 1620w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-1300x867.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-550x367.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-1160x773.jpg 1160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1620px) 100vw, 1620px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;1620\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1080\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201620%201080\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow.jpg 1620w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-1300x867.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-550x367.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/003-product-galaxy-zfold7-blueshadow-1160x773.jpg 1160w\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Samsung\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFinally, let\u0026#39;s put our sights on the biggest mobile carrier in the US—\u003ca href=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/507586-verizon-carrier-lock-period/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/507586-verizon-carrier-lock-period/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eVerizon\u003c/a\u003e. Needless to say, that carrier has deals for you too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e$1,100 off the Z Fold 7, or the Z Flip 7 for free, if you\u0026#39;re on Unlimited Ultimate and trade-in an eligible device in any condition.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eGet a free Z Flip 7 (256GB) if you buy a Z Fold/Flip 7 on Unlimited Ultimate or Unlimited Plus. You must open at least one new line, however.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e$1,000 off the Galaxy Z Fold 7 or Z Flip 7 if you\u0026#39;re a Verizon Business customer who signs up for a new line or upgrades. However, requires an eligible trade-in an a My Biz Plan with $20 monthly add-on spending.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eVerizon will give you six months of Google AI Pro, in addition to the six months Samsung is giving all buyers.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThrough Tecno, Gionee, Vivo, Google, and now Samsung, Ayomide has always been an Android enthusiast. His current partner in crime is a Samsung Galaxy S22 Ultra. You can find him playing Candy Crush or Call of Duty: Mobile, watching movies, and he is a big fan of trivia and quizzes.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch5\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrevious Post\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h5\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-scheme=\"inverse\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg width=\"380\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/